'''Norris robes''' were made from the [[Norris root|roots of the Norris plant]] found on the tropical planet of [[Almar]], supplies of which were generally limited.
Ancient [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] took the roots and made a reddish orange dye from them. The dye made their robes both beautiful, but also energy resistant. This made the Norris robes unique and valuable across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

